Class DialogComponentDoubleRangeBounded

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.node.defaultnodesettings.DialogComponent
      • com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.dialogcomponents.AbstractDialogComponentRangeInput<ChangeableDoubleSpinner,SettingsModelDoubleRangeBounded,java.lang.Double>

  • public class DialogComponentDoubleRangeBounded
extends AbstractDialogComponentRangeInput<ChangeableDoubleSpinner,SettingsModelDoubleRangeBounded,java.lang.Double>
    Dialog component to enter a bound Double range. The values are bounded - the bounds are supplied by the SettingsModelDoubleRangeBounded
    Since:
    1.28.0
    Author:
    S.Roughley knime@vernalis.com
